{"tid":2137617,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惡法陰霾 七成人自我審查  市民unfriend刪po 「最恐怖係人與人不信任」","createTime":"2020-08-03T05:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T05:29:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45a8f59ab0a977001c953a6f5587befeb5f5f7bf","tid":2137617,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/2YY6DCHZWTQXDDVPOJSWG4FICM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2F2YY6DCHZWTQXDDVPOJSWG4FICM%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F5hvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=26a1dea3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200803%2F2YY6DCHZWTQXDDVPOJSWG4FICM%2F&h=14d5f829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200803/2YY6DCHZWTQXDDVPOJSWG4FICM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n惡法陰霾 七成人自我審查 <br />\n市民unfriend刪po 「最恐怖係人與人不信任」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jLkJUUzD85dujIy2-CN0KtN7m0E=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TBHCCUBAMJFE6Q2DGMYPA33CMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjLkJUUzD85dujIy2-CN0KtN7m0E%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTBHCCUBAMJFE6Q2DGMYPA33CMU.jpg&h=e6c85881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nT先生曾帶同光時旗到外地旅行，稱仍會在遊行中揮舞。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【《蘋果》調查】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中聯辦主任駱惠寧多次強調港版國安法只針對極少數人，特首林鄭月娥又稱看不到社會出現大量恐懼。但惡法推出逾月，不僅多人被以言入罪、黃店文宣除下、雜誌停刊、專欄作家擱筆、外媒撤走他方，國安法亦已悄悄在市民心中蒙上陰影。與朋友聚頭，暢所欲言變欲言又止；網絡世界不再無邊無際，Big Brother is watching；藏在床下底的旗幟，也怕成罪證。<br />\n<br />\n本報以問卷形式訪問212。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者：關冠麒<br />\n<br />\n記者在民主派<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。訊安全，其次是刪除社交媒體與反送中運動相關的發文或相片，及銷毀或棄置與反送中運動文宣或紀念品，各有約17%。沒有自我審查行為的只有不足三成。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：99%指司法獨立已死 進入一國一制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白領：同事傾初選驚俾人聽到<br />\n<br />\n在中環寫字樓上班的T先生（化名）過去一年經常參與社會運動。他認為國安法條文太含糊，「好難界定做啲乜嘢係國安法唔容許」，所以生活上沒有自我審查，若再有大型遊行，亦會再到現場揮「光時」旗，除非有日國安法條文寫明口號非法。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。，同事開始少談政治話題。有日T和飯腳在辦公室食外賣，他談到初選，「同事就叫我唔好咁大聲，驚其他人聽到」，有同事又擔心在社交媒體的反政府留言會被秋後算賬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zvKBnY6t4vouxDgi6sDEMPuGFx4=/190x190/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N4S6RVRCTUIBFH3CK7RSPTKDBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzvKBnY6t4vouxDgi6sDEMPuGFx4%3D%2F190x190%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN4S6RVRCTUIBFH3CK7RSPTKDBU.jpg&h=37bcbc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApple憂慮藏書《一九八四》或變禁書。<br />\n<br />\n從。。。。。。。。。。。。。她嘆道：「好似件事唔存在，變咗平行時空。」她常轉發抗爭者訪問，盼學生了解。但後來擔心被批鬥，漸減轉發和討論，「唔知佢會唔會畀阿爸阿媽睇，畀其他老師睇」。到。。。。。。。。。。。。。條法例追溯我」。<br />\n<br />\n「其實最恐怖嗰個係人與人之間嘅不信任感。」Apple家中有本印有「光復香港時代革命」的刊物，有朋友來探訪她時，她會憂慮，「人哋見到我有呢本書，我就會開始驚&hellip;&hellip;就算你同佢係同一陣營，你都唔知佢立場係幾堅定」。<br />\n<br />\n問卷亦詢問受訪者會否續將抗爭融入生活。逾九成半人會繼續撐黃店，逾八成人續杯葛藍店，有逾六成半人會續捐款至6.12基金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qC3FfK-rQVdH3Pwh3JRNZdEoMWE=/1237x1191/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UNBUMXDK3DSBLW2XRUMJYQFZVI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqC3FfK-rQVdH3Pwh3JRNZdEoMWE%3D%2F1237x1191%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUNBUMXDK3DSBLW2XRUMJYQFZVI.gif&h=a4f3212d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MYb-BK1vTu-oXa5mNFSnifJFeKs=/1003x1191/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N2NMYUYP5INMD7XDYTF5IG5KAU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMYb-BK1vTu-oXa5mNFSnifJFeKs%3D%2F1003x1191%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northea